Interface IAbstractRepo

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ILoginRepo, IPaymentRepo, IRecipientRepo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ILoginRepoImpl, IPaymentRepoImpl, IRecipientRepoImpl

    public interface IAbstractRepo
    This is the interface for the repositories of the system. It is the "super interface", and all the entity interfaces are inherited classes of this.
